023/10/Five_Nights_At_Freddys-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em>《玩具熊的五夜后宫》</em>已成为 2023 年万圣节季的票房冠军。</p><p>影片改编自电子游戏系列，讲述了保安迈克·施密特（乔什·哈切森饰）在一家废弃的街机餐厅从事夜间工作，却发现四个在夜间复活的电子动画吉祥物的故事。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/five-nights-at-freddys-review-horror-video-game-3521201">《玩具熊的五夜后宫》评论：披萨店恐怖片并没有带来什么</a></strong></li></ul><p>影片于 10 月底上映后，全球票房收入超过 1.36 亿美元（1.12 亿英镑），而制作预算为 2000 万美元（1650 万英镑）。</p><p>其他演员包括派珀·卢比奥、伊丽莎白·莱尔、玛丽·斯图尔特·马斯特森和马修·利拉德。</p><h2> <em>《玩具熊的</em><em>五夜后宫</em>2》已经宣布了吗？</h2><p>布卢姆豪斯尚未正式宣布续集，但从票房上的巨大成功来看，续集实际上是不可避免的。</p><p> Back in February, Lillard confirmed (via <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MfsMmQR3PDY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WeeklyMTG</a> ) he had signed up for three <em>Five Nights At Freddy’s</em> films, so there&#39;s certainly plans to make it an ongoing film series.</p><p> This page will be updated when a sequel and a release date are officially announced. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="玩具熊的五夜后宫 | 玩具熊的五夜后宫官方预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0VH9WCFV6XQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2> What have the creators said about a sequel?</h2><p> Director Emma Tammi said a potential sequel would likely be based on the second game in the series, released back in 2014.</p><p> “We&#39;re definitely excited to keep making more movies in this world, should we be lucky enough to do that,” Tammi told <a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/five-nights-at-freddys-movie-sequel-director-fnaf-lore-1235770214/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a> . “This one was tied into the first game, and we would probably focus on tying the second one into the second game, and so on and so forth. But anything could happen. We&#39;ll have to see.”</p><p> <em>Five Nights At Freddy’s</em> spans nine mainline games in total, along with several spin-offs. The franchise, created by Scott Cawthon, also consists of multiple novels and comics.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/when-five-nights-at-freddys-2-coming-out-release-date-3528147">When is &#39;Five Nights At Freddy&#39;s 2&#39; coming out?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
